<chapter id="ch-maintenance">
 <title>Maintenance</title><indexterm>
 <primary>maintenance</primary></indexterm>
 <para>
  &susemgr; provides a unique environment not available to any other &ncc;
  customers. In return, &susemgr; also requires maintenance. This chapter
  discusses the procedures that should be followed to carry out
  administrative functions outside of standard use and to apply patches to
  &susemgr;.
 </para>


